=Description=

" not all viral sensations happen by themselves. Sometimes marketers work behind the scenes to “grease the viral wheels.”

Dan Ackerman Greenberg is one of those internet marketers. Back in November, he wrote a guest post on TechCrunch called The Secret Strategies Behind Many “Viral” Videos. In it, he outlines a number of strategies and techniques used by marketers to help online videos go viral.

Nora interviewed Dan about viral video marketing."
